Class NogoodFromSolutions

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.chocosolver.solver.search.loop.monitors.NogoodFromSolutions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMonitorSolution, ISearchMonitor

    public class NogoodFromSolutions
extends Object
implements IMonitorSolution
    Avoid exploring same solutions (useful with restart on solution) Beware : - Must be plugged as a monitor - Only works for integer variables

    This can be used to remove similar/symmetric solutions
